latestPosts.caption:
The two exercises:
1. Balloon Pose-
🎈 Blow up your mouth and keep two fingers on your lips from stopping the air to pass out.
Then push all the air to one side of the face and then gradually to the other side as shown visually above.
And then exhale.
This helps in activating the facial muscles, thus improves the blood circulation💫

2. Fish Pose-
🐟 Pull the cheeks and the corners of the lips inwards, like squeezing them in.
Lean your head backwards.
This exercise will help in stretching and leaning your neck and the regular practice will show the results in your jawline💞
